Description: This package simulates the classic casino game Blackjack with full features. It supports multiple players playing against a dealer and includes key actions like hitting, standing, doubling down, surrendering, splitting, and insurance. You can customize the number of players and decks. It works for both interactive play and testing game logic, making it great for learning or fun.
